[I] Generate text based on a template

[T] Template-GLib is a library to help you generate text based on a template
[T] and user defined state. Template-GLib does not use a language runtime, so
[T] it is safe to use from any GObject-Introspectable language.

[U] https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/template-glib

